reviewText: This is not the 20 anniversary edition.
We ordered this movie with the specific case, 20th anniversary addition, but it is not what we received. Returning! It makes me give a star rating- otherwise it would be zero!

This is NOT what I received. I ordered the 20th Anniversary Collector's Edition, however I received the regular DVD with a hand-typed sticker on the back saying "Princess Bride 20th Anniversary New". Absolutely different! I am sorely disappointed! This is the first time I received the wrong item, anytime that I purchase gifts for others they receive what I order exactly, however, the first time I buy myself a gift, it's a pale imitation of my order.
This is an all time favorite movie. I am a huge fan.
Arrived in perfect condition as promised. A fun film.
